{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create interactive ingredient elements for product pages that integrate with the skincare ingredient tree. Include:
    
    INTERACTIVE ELEMENTS:
    - Ingredient tooltips that appear on hover over ingredient names
    - "Learn More" buttons that link to specific ingredients in the tree
    - Ingredient badges/tags that highlight key ingredients
    - Clickable ingredient lists with hover effects
    
    STYLING:
    - Match Haramoona brand styling: primary blue #3498ff, white #ffffff, dark shade #141615, grey #53585a
    - Use Raleway font for consistency
    - Smooth hover animations and transitions
    - Mobile-responsive design
    
    FUNCTIONALITY:
    - Tooltips showing ingredient benefits, function, and origin
    - Links that open the ingredient tree page with specific ingredient highlighted
    - Ingredient badges that can be clicked to learn more
    - Schema settings to easily add/edit ingredients for each product
    - Support for multiple ingredients per product
    
    TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS:
    - Pure CSS and JavaScript (no external libraries)
    - Accessible design with proper ARIA labels
    - Schema settings for easy ingredient management
    - URL parameters to highlight specific ingredients in the tree
    - Responsive tooltips that work on mobile touch devices
    
    INTEGRATION:
    - Can be added to existing product page templates
    - Works with product metafields for ingredient data
    - Links to the skincare ingredient tree page
